###1
### GET 사용자 홈 디렉터리 (정상)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/home?userName=alice
Accept: application/json

### GET 존재하지 않는 사용자
GET http://localhost:3000/user/home?userName=charlie
Accept: application/json

### GET 빈 값 테스트
GET http://localhost:3000/user/home?userName=
Accept: application/json

###2
### ✅ 정상 검색: 존재하는 제목
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/search?title=Node.js%20Tips
Accept: application/json

### ❌ 존재하지 않는 제목
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/search?title=Unknown%20Post
Accept: application/json

### ❌ 빈 title 값 (400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/search?title=
Accept: application/json

###3
### 이메일이 존재하고 verified=true인 경우
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/email?email=alice@example.com

### 이메일이 존재하고 verified=false인 경우
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/email?email=bob@example.com

### 이메일이 존재하지 않는 경우
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/email?email=notfound@example.com

### 잘못된 요청 (빈 값)
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/email?email=

###4
### 존재하는 책 검색
GET http://localhost:3000/book?isbn=978-0132350884
Accept: application/json

### 존재하는 다른 책 검색
GET http://localhost:3000/book?isbn=978-0201616224
Accept: application/json

### 없는 ISBN 검색 (404 예상)
GET http://localhost:3000/book?isbn=000-0000000000
Accept: application/json

### 빈 isbn 파라미터 (400 예상)
GET http://localhost:3000/book?isbn=
Accept: application/json

