### 정상: employeeId=101
GET http://localhost:3000/employee/salary?employeeId=101

### 정상: employeeId=102
GET http://localhost:3000/employee/salary?employeeId=102

### 없는 직원: employeeId=999
GET http://localhost:3000/employee/salary?employeeId=999

### 빈 employeeId (400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:3000/employee/salary?employeeId=
